import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';

function HomeScreen() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Row>
        <Col>
          <video controls>
            <source src={require('../images/Explosion.mp4')} type="video/mp4" />
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default HomeScreen
